content.chorus:
Cheta m onyenwem, achupula nwaodibo Gi
Cheta m onyenwem, Chukwu Nna moo.
verses:
Chetam Onyenwem, chetanu onye I jiri maka ya taa ahuhu
Cheta m ekwela ka m laa n'iyi.

Cheta m Onyenwem amara Gi ura kee Gi agbun'ihi m
Cheta m Onyenwem onye I huru n'anya

Lee obe Kalvary ebe akpogburu Dinwenu o
Lee obe Kalvary

Cheta ebere Gi Oh Dinwenu
Cheta ebere Gi Chukwu Nna moo
